Package: dory-filename-repairer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Dory extension for filename encoding repair
 This is a Dory extension which repairs filename which uses wrong
 encoding in Dory. This extension provides the context menu for any
 file whose filename uses wrong encoding, so that you cannot read the
 filename in Dory.
 .
 You can find a candidate for filename in context menu or submenu.
 This extension also provides a decoded name for URL encoded filename.
